snippet.title: Dark Deception: Monsters & Mortals Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Dark Deception: Monsters & Mortals is available on Steam on Oct 30th at 12PM PST! Wishlist it now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1266690/Dark_Deception_Monsters__Mortals/

Join this channel to get access to perks:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCUtLsKBsHJSC4xJRdI-i5Eg/join

video editing: Mike Bambridge
music: Daniel Dombrowsky
